Description. Head. Vertex smooth, yellowish; occiput without marks (
Fig. 13
A
); scape pale green, with dark red, longitudinal line laterally not reaching antennal base; pedicel pale green with dorsal black spot laterally; flagellum pale, covered with back bristles, slightly shorter than forewing (
Fig. 13
B
); frons white; gena black; clypeus white, tinged with black laterally; maxillary, labial palpi black (
Fig. 13
C
). Mandibles both with prominent basal tooth (
Fig. 17
D
).

